text:
@SushantJos39350 Will $SIVEF ever go below $4 again? 

Many investors/gurus on X seem highly bullish &amp; laser-focused on this AI photonics/optics theme right now.

The whole “optics is the next AI bottleneck” narrative is gaining serious momentum with names like $MRVL, $CRDO, $LITE, $COHR &amp; $SIVE

